    </div>

    <div class="bento-grid">
      <a class="bento-card bento-feature" href="/checkout/">
        <div class="bento-num">01</div>
        <div class="bento-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="bento-title">Highest ROI: <span class="accent">Google Business Profile</span></h3>
        <h4 class="bento-sub">Every local business. Always. Start here before any other platform.</h4>
        <p class="bento-desc">GBP appears directly in Google search results and Maps — at the moment someone searches for what you offer. Optimized profiles generate 4× more website visits, 12% more calls, and 10% more direction requests. It's free. It's where your customers already are. And most businesses set it up once and never touch it again.</p>
        <ul class="bento-list">
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>46% of all Google searches have local intent — GBP captures them</li>
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Profiles with regular updates appear 2.8× more in top 3 Map results</li>
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>theStacc automates GBP posts + review responses — $49/mo</li>
          <li><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>$1 trial · No contract · First post live in 24 hours</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="bento-mock">
          <div class="bento-mock-bar">
            <div class="bento-mock-meta">THESTACC · AUTOMATES GBP · $49/MO</div>
            <span class="bento-mock-pulse"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="bento-mock-title">GBP posts + review responses + social media — all automated</div>
          <div class="bento-mock-tags">
            <span class="bento-mock-tag brand">$49/mo</span>
            <span class="bento-mock-tag">30 posts/mo</span>
            <span class="bento-mock-tag brand">No contract</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bento-cta">Start the $1 trial <span class="arrow">→</span></div>
      </a>

      <a class="bento-card" href="#platform-2">
        <div class="bento-num">02</div>
        <h3 class="bento-title">Service businesses: Facebook</h3>
